{"tid":1198631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方否認放催淚彈  「煙霧不是來自我們」","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:51:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce179296d65d0ffc6d85f6ccf43571f890c4c2ee","tid":1198631,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"今日（10日）凌晨有示威者試圖衝擊立法會大樓，爆發警民衝突。混亂期間，立法會大樓外一度出現煙霧，多間媒體當時均報稱警方施放了催淚彈。不過警方今日在記者會上否認曾施放催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥今日表示，警方行動中有使用過胡椒噴劑、警棍及催淚水劑。對於有報道指警方曾使用催淚煙，他澄清警方並沒有使用催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n被追問現場為何出現煙霧，他表示：「我都不得而知，相信這（煙霧）不是來自我們的。」"},{"pid":"d0f238e635f5bcc9aa0634d15c1893ffdee8cdd8","tid":1198631,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:45:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"006b1b67604917491a01a48d212a734db27f1817","tid":1198631,"uid":119347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，尋日緊張得滯，放咗個屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3396e625eaae92834ad280a3a72f1b3d4f21e5","tid":1198631,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0f238e635f5bcc9aa0634d15c1893ffdee8cdd8","tid":1198631,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:45:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"縱火就出左滅火筒或者水啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b357afe423f6cdeb819fa44c43643e3c2abe451","tid":1198631,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n扮乜撚野呀"},{"pid":"9323b6e7ccf642c6910f2ee3087350db075238dd","tid":1198631,"uid":232082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLZecI195bvQ&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYD